*.pl:	some perl scripts for generating the xref and the measurements
xref:	reference which symbols are included within FreeCom and which
	files are referenced by this symbol and which other files
	reference the symbol (note: The references are generated per
	file and not individually per symbol)
makefile:	Makefile for DMake v4.1
DOCS\cmt?.txt:	Some comments about my changes in general
DOCS\c0.txt:	Some general comments about Borland's C startup code
